                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>It is reported that B. F. Myers, of the Bedford Gazette, has been nominated
                    as the new Collector of Revenue for the district that includes Franklin county,
                    though the Senate has not yet approved the appointment. No nomination has been
                    made for Assessor. Until the two positions are officially filled, Jeremiah
                    Bowles and A. D. Gordon will continue to carry out their respective duties as
                    Collector and Assessor.</summary>
