                <names/>
                <summary>The article informs readers that Mr. Ashley, in a speech characterized "by
                    exceedingly bad temper and as bad taste," has renewed his efforts in Congress to
                    impeach the President. Such actions, it contends, can only damage "the
                    impeachment programme."</summary>
                <note/>
