                <summary>A thief broke into David F. Leisher's residence on West Market street last
                    Tuesday evening while he and his wife were asleep. The thief absconded with
                    Leisher's pocket-book, which, fortunately for Leisher, was empty. The same
                    night, John Reisner's home was entered illegally, but in this instance the
                    thief, who is thought to be the same person, made off with a silver watch and
